e":"Ali on &#8216;Ilm: No good in silence on beneficial knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Razi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is no good in silence when it comes to knowledge, just as there is no good in speaking when it comes to ignorance.\u201d Source: al-Tafsi\u0304r al-Kabi\u0304r 2:30 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0627\u0632\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34241,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/06\/ali-do-not-rebuke\/","url_meta":{"origin":38271,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Blame: Do not excessively rebuke people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abi al-Sa\u2019ib reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not frequently scold others, for scolding leads to resentment and hatred and too much of it is bad manners.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304\u2019 1\/182 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0628\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-ibn-abu-talib-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":38271,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Curses: Those who curse others are themselves cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubayd al-Kindi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThose who curse others are themselves cursed.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 315 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0646\u062f\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0639\u0644\u064a \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0637\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u200f \u0644\u064f\u0639\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0639\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e 315 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0628\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31704,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/ali-dua-answered-supplication\/","url_meta":{"origin":38271,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Dua: Distance between heaven and earth an answered prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Maslamah ibn Muha